---
/**
 * OnboardingLongActingInsulinScreen — long-acting insulin capture (Your routine
 * 2 of 3). PLAIN DATA CAPTURE — a numeric field, NOT the two-step dose gesture.
 * Generic "long-acting insulin" only (no brand). NO skip valve.
 * Lifted verbatim from `onboarding/long-acting-insulin.html`.
 */
interface Props {
  variant?: "current" | "legacy";
}
---
<div class="content">
  <div class="prog-head">
    <div class="prog-row">
      <button class="back" aria-label="Back">‹</button>
      <span class="title">Your routine</span>
      <span class="count">2 of 3</span>
    </div>
    <div class="prog-dots" role="img" aria-label="Step 2 of 3">
      <span class="d done"></span><span class="d current"></span><span class="d"></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pad" style="margin-top:14px; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; overflow-y:auto;">
    <div class="eyebrow">Your routine · 2 of 3</div>
    <h1 class="title-1" style="font-weight:700; margin:10px 0 0; letter-spacing:-0.015em;">Your long-acting insulin</h1>
    <p class="body muted" style="margin:12px 0 0;">
      Enter the long-acting (basal) insulin dose you take now, exactly as your clinician prescribed it. This is just what you're already on — not a change.
    </p>

    <div class="field">
      <span class="flbl">Long-acting insulin dose, as prescribed</span>
      <div class="fbox">
        <span class="val">14</span>
        <span class="unit">units / day</span>
        <span class="caret" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
      <p class="hint">Your once-daily long-acting insulin. Mealtime/bolus insulin isn't entered here — Luna doesn't touch it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="keypad" aria-hidden="true">
      <button>1</button><button>2</button><button>3</button>
      <button>4</button><button>5</button><button>6</button>
      <button>7</button><button>8</button><button>9</button>
      <button class="blank"></button><button>0</button>
      <button><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ACC1DF" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 4H8l-7 8 7 8h13a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><line x1="18" y1="9" x2="12" y2="15"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="18" y2="15"/></svg></button>
    </div>

    <div style="flex:1; min-height:14px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="pad" style="padding-bottom:8px;">
    <button class="btn primary">Continue</button>
  </div>
</div>
